provenance.note:
Given by Blake sometime between c. 1794 and c. 1803 to the dedicatee Elizabeth Cooper Butts, first wife of Thomas Butts; 
                    passed by inheritance to Butts's daughter by her first marriage, Mary Anne Long; 
                    passed down to Long's grandson, Mr. Owen D. Long; 
                    deposited in the British Library by Long in 1981; 
                    sold by Long to the British Library in July 1985 
                    (Bentley, *Blake Books Supplement* page 106).
